{"tid":1398332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"( 難題 )究竟警察搞事，市民正確途徑可以點做?","createTime":"2019-08-02T18:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T03:36:17.000Z","uid":266203,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"50cf2f680954aadf5a02cab8be0da73f7eb4e3bd","tid":1398332,"uid":266203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:22:52.000Z","msg":"近日警察亂咁做嘢，搞到個城市亂曬，<br />\n究竟喺警察發癲嘅時候，<br />\n例如亂咁闖入私人屋苑搞事，<br />\n亂咁打人，隨手喺街見人就仆，<br />\n仲要屈人襲警，可以點做？&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n就算係市民夾手夾腳捉咗嗰條黑警，<br />\n再有片有證據去起訴呢個差人警察，<br />\n又應該去邊度報案呢，<br />\n根本成班都係佢哋自己友，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔通真係軍政府話曬事？</span></span>"},{"pid":"be58759011ecc03abc6ea5ed38ed9fdde2ab48f7","tid":1398332,"uid":266203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:24:23.000Z","msg":"現時政治環境底下市民的生活難題"},{"pid":"bfcb82e4c483ff78f014e865edcd37f9993e6fce","tid":1398332,"uid":261914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:24:26.000Z","msg":"麻包袋"},{"pid":"0202b1c3796e9f147b48806e6d2dddb90b362950","tid":1398332,"uid":266203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:24:46.000Z","msg":"無助無奈"},{"pid":"8e1cea79ca7f4dfa92b6e85cb112ba366864a69f","tid":1398332,"uid":266203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:25:52.000Z","msg":"軍政府繼續咁玩落去，結局會係點有咩國際歷史參考？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a25b1a318b8049ca3258ea6a6f0029d24a78f5","tid":1398332,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:27:34.000Z","msg":"69開始警察啲衰嘢犯法野慢慢逐日寫<br />\n可以寫滿幾張紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414ec5751d3b5a8ad3a22573d6f6970318b66017","tid":1398332,"uid":266203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:28:02.000Z","msg":"市民欠缺智囊團"},{"pid":"4d04af267307b8b87d73c8cb47b8553c8a135f51","tid":1398332,"uid":189328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"